---
---

<section class="success-stories reveal" id="work">
    <div class="success-stories__header">
        <div class="success-stories__header-ref">
            <span class="success-stories__ref-code">SEC.03</span>
            <span class="success-stories__ref-line"></span>
        </div>
        <p class="success-stories__overline">MISSION LOG</p>
        <h2 class="success-stories__headline">Results</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="success-stories__cards">
        <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-1">
            <div class="success-stories__card-top">
                <span class="success-stories__card-id">LOG—001</span>
                <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Architecture</span>
            </div>
            <span class="success-stories__card-metric">40% cost reduction</span>
            <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SAAS PLATFORM REBUILD</h3>
            <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Architecture overhaul of a multi-tenant SaaS platform serving 200+ enterprise clients. Migrated from monolithic PHP to distributed Node.js, tripling throughput.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-2">
            <div class="success-stories__card-top">
                <span class="success-stories__card-id">LOG—002</span>
                <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Leadership</span>
            </div>
            <span class="success-stories__card-metric">12-person team</span>
            <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">SCALE-UP TEAM BUILDING</h3>
            <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Built an engineering team from scratch. Established hiring pipelines, onboarding, and code review culture that cut deploy time from weeks to hours.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-3">
            <div class="success-stories__card-top">
                <span class="success-stories__card-id">LOG—003</span>
                <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Infrastructure</span>
            </div>
            <span class="success-stories__card-metric">99.99% uptime</span>
            <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">CLOUD MIGRATION</h3>
            <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Migrated a legacy monolith to cloud-native microservices on AWS — zero downtime, 5M records preserved, 60% infrastructure cost reduction.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="success-stories__card stagger stagger-4">
            <div class="success-stories__card-top">
                <span class="success-stories__card-id">LOG—004</span>
                <span class="success-stories__card-tag">Product Dev</span>
            </div>
            <span class="success-stories__card-metric">3x conversions</span>
            <h3 class="success-stories__card-title">E-COMMERCE RELAUNCH</h3>
            <p class="success-stories__card-desc">Rebuilt a failing e-commerce platform end-to-end, delivering 3x conversion rate improvement and 60% faster page loads.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="success-stories__cta-row">
        <a class="success-stories__cta" href="#contact">INITIATE CONTACT</a>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    .success-stories {
        padding: 80px 144px 48px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 40px;

        &__header {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        &__header-ref {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        &__ref-code {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
        }

        &__ref-line {
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--clr-border);
            max-width: 120px;
        }

        &__overline {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.18em;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
        }

        &__headline {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 64px;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            line-height: 0.95;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        &__cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        &__card {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            background: var(--clr-bg-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--clr-border-light);
            padding: 24px 24px 28px;
            position: relative;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease;

            &:hover {
                border-color: var(--clr-accent-dim);
            }
        }

        &__card-top {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        &__card-id {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 9px;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
        }

        &__card-tag {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 9px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
            padding: 2px 8px;
            border: 1px solid var(--clr-accent-dim);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        &__card-metric {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 32px;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-accent);
        }

        &__card-title {
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: var(--clr-text-primary);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        }

        &__card-desc {
            font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: var(--clr-text-muted);
            line-height: 1.65;
            flex: 1;
        }

        &__cta-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        &__cta {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--clr-bg-primary);
            background: var(--clr-accent);
            border-radius: 2px;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            transition: opacity 0.2s ease;

            &:hover {
                opacity: 0.85;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 2rem;

            &__cards {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 375px) {
        .success-stories {
            padding: 64px 1.25rem;
        }
    }
</style>
